data.description: Three bedroom rambler in south Fargo with 2 stall garage! Features include updated kitchen, some newer windows, newer roof, metal soffit and fascia, vinyl siding, etc. Low specials and a large, fully fenced back yard make this a must see. Kitchen has quartz, a mobile island, white cabinets and built-ins. Basement is partially finished with a future 4th bedroom (no egress) and laundry. Washer and Dryer stay. All this for the price of a standard twin home!
